"tlg0007_tlg112.T143745" [label="THES", locus="691c", speaker="Plutarchus", text="οὐκ ἄτοπον, εἰ τὴν ψυχρότητα τοῦ ὕδατος ἀντερείδων συνεπιτείνει καὶ ὁ λίθος καὶ ὁ μόλιβδος", paraphrasis="{It is not strange if} both stone and lead, 'exerting counter-pressure against' {= supporting} the coldness (of the water contained in vessels in which they are plunged), 'tighten' {= intensify} it ", manifestation="explicit", source="tlg0007_tlg112", color="palegreen", label_color="darkseagreen", style="rounded,filled", shape="box", margin="0.30,0.1"];

